      "text": "Venice looks like a beautiful place. My question: what do they do for fresh water and dispose of sewage.",
      "likeCount": 1,
      "publishedAt": "2026-07-04T05:20:18Z",
      "replyCount": 3,
      "replies": [
        {
          "id": "UgxAmZHpTZmX7yqySD14AaABAg.AYpUMRwueorAYxIApzWO0w",
          "author": "@justayoutuber1906",
          "authorImage": "https://yt3.ggpht.com/ytc/AIdro_kQ0A4TQAZbI89qM6cRKMMJQFXiEkdCeKEkx7w68ExELg=s48-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj",
          "text": "People have septic tanks and they are pumped out and carried to the mainland for processing.",
          "likeCount": 0,
          "publishedAt": "2026-07-07T06:07:47Z"
        },
        {
          "id": "UgxAmZHpTZmX7yqySD14AaABAg.AYpUMRwueorAYxI8SNrNzR",
          "author": "@justayoutuber1906",
          "authorImage": "https://yt3.ggpht.com/ytc/AIdro_kQ0A4TQAZbI89qM6cRKMMJQFXiEkdCeKEkx7w68ExELg=s48-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj",
          "text": "@WhereonEarth4K Sewage is NOT dumped in the canals!!!   People have septic tanks and they are pumped out and carried to the mainland for processing.",
          "likeCount": 0,
          "publishedAt": "2026-07-07T06:07:27Z"
        },
        {
          "id": "UgxAmZHpTZmX7yqySD14AaABAg.AYpUMRwueorAYqZQT3Wq7P",
          "author": "@WhereonEarth4K",
          "authorImage": "https://yt3.ggpht.com/eGYI9iH4DF7Eb8QJYMMO2qNL_ls-4aNbWgY0tHLbCMrP4phySA3gN8SnhWB02TzySTEBGRXAIg=s48-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj",
          "text": "Venice draws fresh water via underwater aqueducts from the mainland, and much of the old city still relies on the tidal flush — twice a day the Adriatic effectively rinses the canals. It's one of the oldest engineering bargains the city still runs on.",
